and isolate someone.

123
00:11:36.697 --> 00:11:37.698
Immediately.

124
00:11:39.074 --> 00:11:43.160
<i>I'm here on the street just
outside the Westacres shopping center.</i>

125
00:11:43.161 --> 00:11:46.373
