I went through his pockets.

144
00:12:47.226 --> 00:12:51.020
He had a return ticket to France.
a café receipt for Le Blanc Russe.

145
00:12:51.021 --> 00:12:52.939
which is White Russian...
don't say anything...

146
00:12:52.940 --> 00:12:54.941
