202
00:15:45.946 --> 00:15:48.155
Yes. sorry.

203
00:15:48.156 --> 00:15:51.493
No. that's fine. Shall I drop you here?

204
00:15:52.286 --> 00:15:53.662
Yes.

205
00:15:59.793 --> 00:16:03.088
95 euros. please.

206
